From the number I wore to the city I live in, 11/11 will always be a day of unique and meaningful tribute. Being able to spend time with Veterans - past, present and future – was and is one of the greatest honors of my life. America truly is the land of the free and home of the brave because of you. Remembering all who served. Happy #VeteransDay ! 🇺🇸🇺🇸
 
“Our debt to the heroic men and valiant women in the service of our country can never be repaid. They have earned our undying gratitude. America will never forget their sacrifices.” -Harry Truman
